<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV112">
<l>vāḷkaḷāki nāḷkaḷcella nōymaikuṉṟi mūppeyti</l>
<l>māḷunāḷa tātalālva ṇaṅkivāḻtteṉ ṉeñcamē</l>
<l>āḷatāku naṉmaiyeṉṟu naṉkuṇarnta taṉṟiyu</l>
<l>mīḷvilāta pōkamnalka vēṇṭumāla pātamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the days pass turning into swords, [our bodies] drooping [due to] illnesses,</l>
<l rend="indent">reaching old age,</l>
<l>That day of death [has come]. Therefore, o my heart! Bow to and praise [Him]!</l>
<l>Besides, [with us] understanding well that goodness lies in being [His] servant,</l>
<l>Māl’s feet should bestow [upon us] the enjoyment with no return.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
